## Context

1. Indicate the affected section (i.e. top-level folder)

Getting Started
Build Tools
Syntax
Design Pattern

2. Indicate what kind of issue this is

Bug = a problem that needs to be corrected
Enhancement = a new idea that can be documented/filed
ToResearch = a link you want me to investigate

3. If it applies, indicate the file to which you are referring using non-numerical-ordering names

Instead of: "00-Getting-Started/01-Install-Guide.md"
Write: "Getting Started/Install Guide.md"

For example:

```
Section:
  Getting Started

Issue Type:
  Bug

Folder/File(s):
  - Getting Started/Install Guide.md
  - Getting Started/The REPL.md

```

